---
interface Props {
  lang?: string;
}
const { lang = 'zh-TW' } = Astro.props;
const isEn = lang === 'en';
---

<section class="section warm" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-h">
      {isEn ? 'About Us' : '關於我們'}
      <span class="accent">about</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        {isEn ? (
          <>
            <p>
              We are an advocacy group led primarily by second-generation immigrants in Taiwan.
              Our members' mothers or fathers came from Southeast Asia and Chinese-speaking countries —
              immigrants who came to Taiwan and put down roots.
            </p>
            <p>
              As both Taiwanese youth and children of immigrants, we pay attention to migrant worker
              issues in Taiwanese society, and to the diversity of new residents and second-generation
              immigrant communities in Taiwan.
            </p>
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            <p>
              我們是一個由在臺移民第二代為主體所組成的倡議團體，團體的成員，母親或父親來自東南亞與華語世界的不同國家，是來到台灣落地生根的移民。
            </p>
            <p>
              我們以同時作為臺灣青年與移民二代的視角，關注台灣社會的移民工議題，以及台灣社會的新住民、新二代群體的多樣性。
            </p>
          </>
        )}
      </div>

      <div class="about-origins">
        <div class="about-origins-label">our origins</div>
        <div class="about-origins-list">
          <span>越南</span><span>中國</span><span>泰國</span><span>印尼</span>
          <span>菲律賓</span><span>馬來西亞</span><span>柬埔寨</span><span>寮國</span><span>緬甸</span>
        </div>

        <div class="values-grid">
          {['對話', '人權', '倡議', '共榮'].map(v => (
            <div class="value-chip">{v}</div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    padding: 56px 32px;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .section.warm {
    background: var(--cream-warm);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-h {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .section-h::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--terra);
    align-self: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .accent {
    color: var(--terra-deep);
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .about-origins {
    background: white;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--terra);
  }

  .about-origins-label {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--terra-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-origins-list {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .about-origins-list span:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: ' · ';
    color: var(--terra);
    margin: 0 6px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .value-chip {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--terra-deep);
    background: var(--cream-warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* ── Mobile (≤768px) ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .section-h {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .accent {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .about-text p {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .about-origins-list {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>
